last_episode_to_air.overview: Obi-Wan is drawn into a confrontation with Vader, as Luke's fate hangs in the balance.

name: Obi-Wan Kenobi
overview: During the reign of the Galactic Empire, former Jedi Master, Obi-Wan Kenobi, embarks on a crucial mission to confront allies turned enemies and face the wrath of the Empire.
tagline: Between darkness and defeat, hope survives.

episodes.name: Part I
episodes.overview: Obi-Wan Kenobi lives a humble existence on Tatooine. Despite the dangers of being a Jedi survivor at the height of the Empire, Kenobi is forced to emerge from hiding.

episodes.name: Part II
episodes.overview: Obi-Wan’s mission brings him to a crime-ridden world, home to all manner of scum and villainy.

episodes.name: Part III
episodes.overview: Obi-Wan searches for allies as he attracts the attention of the Empire, threatening the locals.

episodes.name: Part IV
episodes.overview: Obi-Wan Kenobi plots a daring mission into enemy territory.

episodes.name: Part V
episodes.overview: Obi-Wan plans his next move as the Empire, closing in, tries to draw him out.

episodes.name: Part VI
episodes.overview: Obi-Wan is drawn into a confrontation with Vader, as Luke's fate hangs in the balance.
